  "commit_message": "fix(bundle-source): point ./exported.js export at the file that exists\n\nThe `./exported.js` subpath has pointed at `./exported.js` (package root)\nsince 2022, but no such file has ever existed — not in the source tree,\nnot in any published tarball on npm (verified against 4.3.0). The\nprepack pipeline that was in place at the time didn't generate it\neither; it was a dangling reference from day one. Consumers importing\n`@endo/bundle-source/exported.js` would have hit ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND,\nwhich is ",
